sequenceDiagram
    participant C as A chapter
    participant K as Knowledge phase
    participant F as Podcast framing
    participant R as Reader markers
    K->>C: read once
    C-->>K: text + structure + citations
    Note over K: extract verses, terms,<br/>names, concepts
    K->>F: author the conversational framing
    K->>R: emit verse + term markers
    Note over F,R: one read, two outputs —<br/>the chapter is never re-read
